        {
            "title": "台股成功四連升 今收漲1.6% 單周累計升8.74%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股連升4個交易日，台灣加權指數今且以全日高位收市，報35417點，升556點或1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數本周累計共漲2845點或8.74%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15856341-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e5%9b%9b%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87-%e4%bb%8a%e6%94%b6%e6%bc%b21-6-%e5%96%ae%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e5%8d%878-74",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230704_FI_source-licensed_TaiwanStock.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 13:42:10",
